"Verifiquemos las inferencias contrafactuales."

#: ../source/notebooks/customer_choice/nested_logit.ipynb:240002
#: ee90dd035c074a138475c7b62065dc98
msgid "Making Interventions in Structured Markets"
msgstr "Realizando intervenciones en mercados estructurados"

#: ../source/notebooks/customer_choice/nested_logit.ipynb:260002
#: 4f30886244a541b3b692ec1a7ce957d7
msgid ""
"Here we can see that both nesting structures recover non-proportional "
"patterns of product substitution. We have elided the IIA feature of the "
"multinomial logit and can continue to assess whether or not the behaviour "
"implications of these utility theory makes sense."
msgstr ""
"Aquí podemos ver que ambas estructuras de anidamiento recuperan patrones de "
"sustitución de productos no proporcionales. Hemos elidido la característica "
"IIA del logit multinomial y podemos continuar evaluando si las implicaciones"
" de comportamiento de esta teoría de la utilidad tienen sentido."

#: ../source/notebooks/customer_choice/nested_logit.ipynb:290002
#: f6d50517fb7e4cc28e21d7bbb803844a
